## Spiral generator

The Spiral shot combines orbit motion with vertical and optionally radial motion.

Suggested parameters:

* Start radius
* End radius
* Start height
* End height
* Revolutions
* Direction
* Duration
* FOV start
* FOV end
* Easing
* Look ahead
* Maintain target size
* Collision avoidance

Suggested formula:

```text
progress = easing(t / duration)

radius = lerp(startRadius, endRadius, progress)
height = lerp(startHeight, endHeight, progress)
angle = startAngle + directionSign * revolutions * 2 * PI * progress

cameraX = targetX + radius * cos(angle)
cameraY = targetY + height
cameraZ = targetZ + radius * sin(angle)
```

Support:

* Spiral inward
* Spiral outward
* Spiral upward
* Spiral downward
* Combined vertical and radial spiral

Reject values that would place the camera inside the target bounding volume.

