## Framing score

Create a framing scoring model:

```text
framingScore =
    visibilityWeight * visibilityScore
    + safeAreaWeight * safeAreaScore
    + coverageWeight * coverageScore
    + compositionWeight * compositionScore
    + groupWeight * groupCoverageScore
    + directionWeight * vehicleDirectionScore
    - clippingPenalty
    - excessiveDistancePenalty
    - excessiveCloseupPenalty
```

